                          <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<h2>Two front wheel options</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><div></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/DTSwiss_Dynamo_Hub_Detail_SP_PL_7_Hub_G_1800_GR_1600_002_1920px-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Dt Swiss Dynamo hub\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/DTSwiss_Dynamo_Hub_Detail_SP_PL_7_Hub_G_1800_GR_1600_002_1920px-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/DTSwiss_Dynamo_Hub_Detail_SP_PL_7_Hub_G_1800_GR_1600_002_1920px-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/DTSwiss_Dynamo_Hub_Detail_SP_PL_7_Hub_G_1800_GR_1600_002_1920px-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/DTSwiss_Dynamo_Hub_Detail_SP_PL_7_Hub_G_1800_GR_1600_002_1920px-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/DTSwiss_Dynamo_Hub_Detail_SP_PL_7_Hub_G_1800_GR_1600_002_1920px-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/DTSwiss_Dynamo_Hub_Detail_SP_PL_7_Hub_G_1800_GR_1600_002_1920px-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/DTSwiss_Dynamo_Hub_Detail_SP_PL_7_Hub_G_1800_GR_1600_002_1920px-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/DTSwiss_Dynamo_Hub_Detail_SP_PL_7_Hub_G_1800_GR_1600_002_1920px-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/DTSwiss_Dynamo_Hub_Detail_SP_PL_7_Hub_G_1800_GR_1600_002_1920px-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/DTSwiss_Dynamo_Hub_Detail_SP_PL_7_Hub_G_1800_GR_1600_002_1920px.jpg 1920w\" /><figcaption>Dt Swiss</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Laced into the GR 1600 Spline alloy front wheel with 24 straight-pull DT Aero Comp spokes, DT’s dynamo has a total claimed front wheel weight of 1,075g. Dynamo front wheel prices start at $442.90 / €320.90.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alternatively, the G 1800 Spline Dyn front wheel also has an alloy rim. Its weight is claimed at 1,098g and it’s priced at $342.90 / €258.90. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Both wheels are tubeless-ready and supplied ready-taped and with valves and lighting connectors.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also buy the dynamo and build up your own wheels. On its own, it has a claimed 376g weight and is priced at $236.90 / €174.90.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the UK, the two wheel options will be available to order from UK distributor Madison, priced at £299.99 and £234.99.</p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-all-road-bikes\">Best all-road bikes 2024 reviewed</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/garmin-varia-rear-view-radar-review\">Garmin Varia rear view radar review</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-gravel-bike\">The best gravel bikes 2024 reviewed</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/buyers-guide-the-best-gravel-bike-tyres\">Best gravel bike tyres 2024 and how to choose the right ones</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-bike-lights\">Best bike lights 2024 reviewed: Front and rear light sets rated</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/buyers-guide-best-winter-cycling-socks\">Best winter cycling socks 2024: Keep your feet warm while riding in the cold</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div><p>The post <a href=\"https://